reviewText: This product/movie was too commercial sounding. Did not make me want to visit New Zealand. Maybe they needed a better spokesperson?..

I was disappointed by this DVD.  The narrator had a very flat boring voice and the DVD was fairly short for what I was expecting.  Tried to get my son and husband engaged to watch and they were both underwhelmed.  I also bought "Kiwi Country New Zealand" which was far superior and contained alot more quality video and exciting narration and video.
